lead_paragraph: Fabio Borini scored a crucial stoppage-time equaliser to ensure Sunderland earned a draw which pulled them out of the Premier League relegation zone on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Borini Earns Big Point for Sunderland After Wickham Brace
